 into service only when needed for ease of connected, penlift-avoiding 
writing.&#160; I don&#39;t think this &#34;new&#34; letter can be confused with any 
existing letter forms.&#160; It&#39;s easily-recognizable as a &#34;backwards&#34; L.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Another
